OL,5, Unavoidable hidden charges for online  
OL,6, customers, or "drip pricing", is set to
OL,7, be banned under new law proposals.     
OL,9,FFake reviews will also be banned and   
OL,10,Ffirms will have to be clearer with     
OL,11,Fprice labels on supermarket shelves.   
OL,13,FIt follows a government consultation on
OL,14,Fconsumer transparency that found some  
OL,15,Fbusinesses are not as clear as they    
OL,16,Fcould be about prices.                 
OL,18,FThe new rules will form part of the    
OL,19,FDigital Markets, Competition and       
OL,20,FConsumers Bill.                        
